&lt;p&gt;Collaborate daily with a cross-disciplinary team to design the interface between the orchestration system, matchmaking systems, and internal developer experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Effectively write clear, concise, and accurate technical documentation and email communication, with the ability to summarize complex topics and achieve alignment across multiple teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Calmly deal with production incidents, participating in an on-call rotation after launch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
