&lt;li&gt;Ensure visual aspects of the game are performant across all platforms (PC, console)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with project leadership to define and oversee the Technical Art roadmap, working cross team with technical artists, animators &amp;amp; designers to inform these decisions&lt;/li&gt;
