&lt;li&gt;Develop and refine workflows and pipelines that boost production efficiency and foster team collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Introduce new features to the art team by showcasing examples, giving presentations, and producing relevant documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in proactive communication with all stakeholders to ensure shared objectives and preemptively manage any challenges.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
